Excludes Plus Fees

**Note:
Global Total includes PNR, EDAs, Connectors, and Resell + Sell-To ACV via Strategic HLS Partnerships (Optum, Cerner, IQVia)
PNR = Percent of Net Revenue via traditional OEM / ISVForce sales (FY19 Target = $132.5M)
Takeoff - ACV based on HQ region of Partner
Landing - ACV based on End Customer location, regardless of Partner

**Note:
IQVIA includes $2.1M BPO deal closed in Q2 & $3.5M EDA closed in Q3
Amadeus $1.8M EDA included in FY18 baseline (PNR 12% YoY)
